00:47:18.730 --> 00:47:21.650
If you are interested in
a quantum state and it

00:47:21.650 --> 00:47:23.240
decays to a level.

00:47:23.240 --> 00:47:25.340
But we're not really
interested what this level is

00:47:25.340 --> 00:47:27.215
and we're not keeping
track of the population

00:47:27.215 --> 00:47:32.630
here, when we can describe the
