00:48:19.950 --> 00:48:21.610
but in incoherent way.

00:48:21.610 --> 00:48:24.240
So what is being built
up in the ground state

00:48:24.240 --> 00:48:25.760
is not a wave function.

00:48:25.760 --> 00:48:28.850
